&lt;p class=&quot;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a talented and passionate&lt;strong&gt; Game Designer &amp;amp; Game Lead&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Wildlife&#39;s New Games team&lt;/strong&gt;. Wildlife is constantly building and releasing new titles with the goal of bringing fun to billions of people around the world. The company has already surpassed the mark of 4 billion downloads. The New Games Product team is accountable for defining which new games will be produced and building these products in partnership with engineers and artists. These are the products that will drive the company&#39;s growth for the following years.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
