&lt;li&gt;Experience in product or game design roles within game development (shipping games in any platform, leading product development in game jams or hackathons)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about games, you have been a player your whole life&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to work in iterative development cycles with frequent releases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong data analysis skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
