&lt;li&gt;Excited about joining the most valuable, highest growth start-up in Brazil that will provide you meaningful work, meaningful relationships, continuous meaningful learning, and a team radically committed to produce great products;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thoughtful and analytical decision-maker: you consider

