&lt;li class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory: Expected graduation between July 2027 and December 2027. Applications outside this window will not be considered.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
